### **2. 24_APIRelayWatch**  
**Description:**  
Monitors latency and uptime across API relays or proxy clusters in real-time.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# APIRelayWatch - Multi-Relay Endpoint Tracker

APIRelayWatch provides visibility into health and response metrics of APIs behind relay layers.

## Features
- Logs response time and HTTP code  
- CSV or JSON export  
- Retry and timeout support  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/24_APIRelayWatch.git
cd 24_APIRelayWatch
python monitor.py
